Sue Holderness https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sue_Holderness 0 Susan Joan Pringle Holderness (born 28 May 1949) is an English actress. She played the role of Marlene Boyce in the British sitcom Only Fools and Horses (from 1985 to 2003) and its spin-off The Green Green Grass (from 2005 until 2009).
